'''Walulis sieht fern''' (English: ''Walulis watches TV'') is a satirical German television show broadcast on [[Digital television|digital television channel]] [[EinsPlus]]. The show was created and is presented by its namesake, [[Philipp Walulis]].<ref>{{de icon}}[http://www.zeit.de/kultur/film/2012-03/walulis-grimme-preis Zeit.de-Artikel]</ref> It parodies German television under the motto "Fernsehen macht blöd, aber auch unglaublich viel Spaß!" (''TV makes you stupid, but also is incredibly much fun!'')
